====[[Robbery of the ReadyQuick Check Cashing|ReadyQuick Cashing Robbery]]====
[[File:JigsawLeavingJNelson-RobPrep.png|{{AltFloat}}|Russo heading out of the crew's hideout]]
{{Quote|There's not one person in this place who believes that that door is on a timer. So trust me, when I tell you that today is not the day to do this. So give some thought to why you wanna see tomorrow, and open the damn door.|Jigsaw to [[Lillian (Manager)|Lillian]]|One Bad Day}}
