[[File:Jigsaw-KillsTwoOfHisCrew.png|{{AltFloat}}|Russo killing [[Bobby (Jigsaw's Crew)|two]] [[Anton Reed|people]] to silence his [[Jigsaw's Crew|crew]]]]
